description: Gyropedia.com is an Association of people who fly, build or regulate Gyroplanes, who have a dream of a single Gyroplane pilot licence accepted in every country around the world, and a community of Gyroplane Pilots who are free from accidents. This quiz allows Student pilots and licenced pilots to challenge their own knowledge of flying these wonderful aircraft.
exampleInteractions: Alexa ask gyropedia questions to start quiz
name: Gyropedia Quiz
shortDescription: Gyropedia Quiz.  Challenge yourself to answer 5 random questions on gyroplane knowledge.
